{"_path":"/maps/_ai/rag","_dir":"_ai","_draft":false,"_partial":true,"_locale":"","title":"RAG (检索增强生成)","description":"","body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h1","props":{"id":"rag-检索增强生成"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"RAG (检索增强生成)"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"chroma轻量级嵌入式向量数据库"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Chroma：轻量级嵌入式向量数据库"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Chroma 是最易上手的向量数据库，主打\"嵌入式\"——直接 pip 安装，无需额外服务。适合原型验证和中小规模应用（< 1000 万向量），提供直观的 Python API，与 LangChain、LlamaIndex 无缝集成。对于需要快速启动的 AI 应用，Chroma 是零成本入门的首选。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.trychroma.com/","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Chroma 官网"}]},{"type":"text","value":" | "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.truefoundry.com/blog/best-vector-databases","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"2025 最佳向量数据库"}]},{"type":"text","value":" | "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://en.paperblog.com/vector-databases-for-rag-pinecone-vs-weaviate-vs-chroma-2025-comparison-guide-8014057/","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"RAG 向量数据库对比"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"faissfacebook-高效相似度搜索库"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"FAISS：Facebook 高效相似度搜索库"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"FAISS 是 Facebook 开源的向量搜索库，提供多种索引算法：Flat（精确搜索，小数据集）、IVF（倒排文件索引，平衡速度/精度）、HNSW（图索引，高维大数据集最优）、PQ（乘积量化，极致压缩）。适合需要精细控制索引算法、已有数据基础设施只需向量搜索模块、大规模数据集（十亿级向量）的场景。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://github.com/facebookresearch/faiss","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"FAISS GitHub"}]},{"type":"text","value":" | "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://github.com/facebookresearch/faiss/wiki/Guidelines-to-choose-an-index","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"FAISS 索引选择指南"}]},{"type":"text","value":" | "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://milvus.io/blog/understanding-ivf-vector-index-how-It-works-and-when-to-choose-it-over-hnsw.md","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"HNSW vs IVF 对比"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"qdrantrust-实现的开源向量数据库"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Qdrant：Rust 实现的开源向量数据库"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Qdrant 是用 Rust 编写的向量数据库，性能优异且功能丰富：过滤搜索（向量相似度 + 元数据过滤同时进行）、混合搜索（稀疏向量 + 密集向量结合）、量化（Scalar、Product 量化降低内存 97%）、分布式原生支持集群部署。适合生产级 RAG 应用。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://qdrant.tech/","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Qdrant 官网"}]},{"type":"text","value":" | "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://qdrant.tech/documentation/concepts/hybrid-queries/","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Qdrant 混合搜索"}]},{"type":"text","value":" | "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://qdrant.tech/documentation/guides/quantization/","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Qdrant 量化指南"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"sentence-transformers文本嵌入模型库"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Sentence Transformers：文本嵌入模型库"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Sentence Transformers（SBERT）是生成文本嵌入的事实标准库，提供预训练模型（all-MiniLM、all-mpnet 等）、多语言支持、微调接口，与向量数据库无缝集成。all-MiniLM-L6-v2 是最流行的轻量级模型，将句子映射到 384 维向量空间。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.sbert.net/","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Sentence Transformers 文档"}]},{"type":"text","value":" | "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.sbert.net/docs/sentence_transformer/pretrained_models.html","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"预训练模型列表"}]},{"type":"text","value":" | "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://sbert.net/examples/sentence_transformer/training/multilingual/README.html","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"多语言模型"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"rag-进阶技术"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"RAG 进阶技术"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"多向量检索：句子窗口（存储段落，检索句子 + 上下文）、父子块（小块用于匹配，大块用于生成）、摘要索引（用摘要辅助长文档检索）。查询优化：查询扩展（用 LLM 生成同义查询）、HyDE（生成假设文档，用其嵌入检索）、路由（根据查询类型选择不同检索策略）。Agentic RAG 结合 Agent 能力实现多跳推理、子问题分解、工具使用。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.truefoundry.com/blog/best-vector-databases","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"RAG 最佳实践指南"}]},{"type":"text","value":" | "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://github.com/zilliztech/VectorDBBench","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"VectorDB Bench 性能测试"}]}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[{"id":"chroma轻量级嵌入式向量数据库","depth":2,"text":"Chroma：轻量级嵌入式向量数据库"},{"id":"faissfacebook-高效相似度搜索库","depth":2,"text":"FAISS：Facebook 高效相似度搜索库"},{"id":"qdrantrust-实现的开源向量数据库","depth":2,"text":"Qdrant：Rust 实现的开源向量数据库"},{"id":"sentence-transformers文本嵌入模型库","depth":2,"text":"Sentence Transformers：文本嵌入模型库"},{"id":"rag-进阶技术","depth":2,"text":"RAG 进阶技术"}]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:6.maps:_ai:rag.md","_source":"content","_file":"6.maps/_ai/rag.md","_stem":"6.maps/_ai/rag","_extension":"md"}